import React from 'react'
import '../styles.css'
const Main = () => {
  return (
    <main className="main">
      <form className="form">
        <label for="email" className="label">
          Email:
          <input placeholder="email" id="email" className="email" />
        </label>
        <label className="label">
          Password:
          <input
            for="password"
            placeholder="password"
            id="password"
            className="email"
          />
        </label>
        <button>pic</button>
      </form>
    </main>
  )
}

export default Main
